    ∇ End;tempfiles
    ⍝ Called by destructor
      :Access Public
      Logger.Stop ⍬
      :If 0=⎕NC'ServerName'
         ⍝!!! {}1 #.DRC.Init''
      :Else
          'Not running'⎕SIGNAL(#.DRC.Exists ServerName)↓11
          {}#.DRC.Close ServerName
