    ∇ r←SpaceName cmd
     ⍝ Generate namespace name from command name
      r←'Common.C',Subst(2⊃{1↓¨('.'=⍵)⊂⍵}'.',cmd)'-=' '_∆'
    ∇

    ∇ r←Subst arg;i;m;str;c;rep
      ⍝ Substitute character c in str with rep
      str c rep←arg
      i←c⍳str
      m←i≤⍴c
      (m/str)←rep[m/i]
      r←str
    ∇

    ∇ file←Config Virtual page;mask;f;ind;t;path;root
